comments: Very nice guy, his class was easy, but you still learned! I really wish I had taken him for 132 as well!
Amazing I just took his class last semester and it was awesome. He is super helpful and has fun teaching the class.

I love this teacher. I took him for 131 also. I tell all of my friends to take him because he is a great teacher and that he is really easy. He doesn\'t give out homework. The only homework are your essays.
He is a really nice guy. Honestly though i felt more like i was in a philosophy class then english sometimes. Overall he will help you if you need it. Good teacher.

he is very down to earth. he explains everything very clearly. gives you the grades you work for, so if you try you will get a good grade. he makes class interesting and relates it to everyday life. i enjoy going to his class everyday!!!:)
He is a cool teacher. Tries to make class fun and it is cool how he makes conceps accessible by relating them to real life situations or situations we can understand. I hightly recomend him.
